量，可能會導致北京辣手損害美國在全球的利益，這是我們的評估。」<br />\n<br />\n佢無話要縮 只係分析話中國會全球搞鳩美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ed407816d8de2b9a357767b6c7761d1fe083b9","tid":2510372,"uid":256143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57b25f8da449e029688869c5d7f3e661b3ca6c7","tid":2510372,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"個標題做乜野 , 記者唔識 summary 唔該讀多啲書先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"記者想引起罵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df34fd69a5eaa4ff545b8d44005d0964cd01941b","tid":2510372,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c442d7286171adb02a3d3d67a7715d7ca0ca75","tid":2510372,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"講撚中咗 美國已經有走返返去appeasement policy"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"你睇篇文講up先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地係分析會對美國利益有影響，同講呀媽係女人有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n根本美國介唔介入都會有影響，係睇邊樣令自己有最大利益，美國護台從來都唔係無條件支持"},{"pid":"ca9a2b448137b9b731e8d4a99db7c423b1d24fc3","tid":2510372,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57b25f8da449e029688869c5d7f3e661b3ca6c7","tid":2510372,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"個標題做乜野 , 記者唔識 summary 唔該讀多啲書先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"NOW，你懂的"},{"pid":"cdd51ff8e8294f315091793722e7bfb2a2c7e5b9","tid":2510372,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df34fd69a5eaa4ff545b8d44005d0964cd01941b","tid":2510372,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c442d7286171adb02a3d3d67a7715d7ca0ca75","tid":2510372,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"講撚中咗 美國已經有走返返去appeasement policy"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T07:37:12.000Z","msg"